data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This exquisite house features all the amenities you desire, offering a relaxed and comfortable living experience. This house boasts three well-appointed bedrooms with two full bathrooms and an additional half bathroom, there's no shortage of convenience. The main suite is a true oasis, featuring his and hers closest, ensuring ample storage space. You'll enjoy the privacy of the commode and the luxury of a standalone shower. It even includes a cozy sitting area, perfect for relaxation. The home offers a comfortable living room, ideal for entertaining friends or spending quality time with loved ones. Outside, you'll find a sparkling pool, perfect for both exercise and relaxation. The accompanying entertaining area makes hosting barbecues or outdoor gatherings a delight. Whether you want to lounge poolside, soak up the sun, or dine al fresco, this space caters to your every need. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this incredible house.
